 Subject will be followed for 1 year and will be seen three times for measurements.

 Study population: 100 subjects, ages 50 and older with drusen and/or Retinal pigment epithelium (RPE) alterations on retinal image.

 Main study parameters/endpoints: Changes in amount of early macular degeneration signs on fundus photographs.

 Macular pigment optical density.

